OL,3,CMan Utd's Ella Toone and darts
OL,4,Cchampion Luke Littler to receive MBEs
OL,6,FTeenage darts prodigy Luke Littler and
OL,7,FEngland midfielder Ella Toone will be
OL,8,Famong the stars to be honoured at an
OL,9,Finvestiture ceremony.
OL,11,FComedian Matt Lucas, Wicked star
OL,12,FCynthia Erivo and England rugby union
OL,13,Fplayer Sadia Kabeya are also among the
OL,14,F66 people who are due to receive their
OL,15,Fhonours at Windsor Castle on Tuesday,
OL,16,F19 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
