OL,3,CMan Utd's Ella Toone and darts
OL,4,Cchampion Luke Littler to receive MBEs
OL,6,FMeanwhile, actress and singer Cynthia
OL,7,FErivo was made an MBE in the New Year
OL,8,FHonours list for services to music and
OL,9,Fdrama.
OL,11,FThe Wicked star, from Stockwell, south
OL,12,FLondon, has already won a Grammy,
OL,13,FDaytime Emmy, Tony and has been
OL,14,Fnominated for an Oscar.
OL,16,FThe 39-year-old, who has appeared on
OL,17,FBroadway and the West End, trained at
OL,18,Fthe prestigious Royal Academy of
OL,19,FDramatic Art, graduating with a
OL,20,Fbachelor's degree in acting in 2010.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
