PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779203471
OL,3,CMan Utd's Ella Toone and darts
OL,4,Cchampion Luke Littler to receive MBEs
OL,6,FShe achieved worldwide fame after
OL,7,Fstarring as the green witch Elphaba in
OL,8,Fthe two-part film version of the
OL,9,Fmusical Wicked alongside pop star
OL,10,FAriana Grande.
OL,12,FSpeaking in December, Erivo said: "To
OL,13,Fbe given this recognition to celebrate
OL,14,Fthe work that I love to do within the
OL,15,Farts, specifically music and drama, is
OL,16,Fan honour I could never have thought
OL,17,Fwould happen.
OL,19,F"I hope it shows that I care deeply
OL,20,Fabout the work and will continue to do
OL,21,Fso to the best of my abilities."
OL,26,@tD@cOU{D@AOU}D@`O]
